One router with 3 pcs in the same lan. The assignment is: to follow
the RIPE NCC IPv6 security slides.

After running radvd in r1 check that all the pcs of the topology
have GUA addresses.

In pc1 and pc2, copy shared/thc.zip and shared/master.zip in the home,
unzip them and run make install inside the extracted directories. 

In pc3 there is scapy.
